# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:53
translate spanish hwb_s04_5c907303:

    # "The sun has long since set and given way to darkness. Only my headlights remain, illuminating the road and silhouetting the small rock formations around us."
    "El sol se ha puesto hace tiempo y ha dado paso a la oscuridad. Solo quedan mis faros, iluminando el camino y silueteando las pequeñas formaciones rocosas a nuestro alrededor."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:55
translate spanish hwb_s04_11052f8d:

    # "I’ve been alternating between the old tape and new ones, immediately throwing on the old tape after finishing a new one and vice versa."
    "He estado alternando entre el casete viejo y los nuevos, poniendo el viejo justo después de terminar uno nuevo y viceversa."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:57
translate spanish hwb_s04_416a997d:

    # "I haven’t had any complaints from Marina. She’s been sitting at my side the entire time, softly humming off-key to the music."
    "No he tenido ninguna queja de Marina. Ha estado sentada a mi lado todo el tiempo, tarareando suavemente y desafinando con la música."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:59
translate spanish hwb_s04_6f84f193:

    # "She seems to be the type to just accept things as they are. Like with her car being stolen or that treasure."
    "Parece ser del tipo que acepta las cosas tal como son. Como lo de que le robaran el coche o ese tesoro."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:61
translate spanish hwb_s04_bb0e65a8:

    # "Especially that treasure."
    "Especialmente ese tesoro."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:63
translate spanish hwb_s04_62af5567:

    # "And to make it worse, it’s not just her. Apparently it’s some phenomenon now."
    "Y para colmo, no es solo ella. Aparentemente ahora es un fenómeno."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:65
translate spanish hwb_s04_da3937ff:

    # "Goes to show how much I keep up with current events."
    "Eso demuestra lo al día que estoy con las noticias."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:67
translate spanish hwb_s04_d4ba797e:

    # "But the whole thing smells like a scam."
    "Pero todo esto huele a estafa."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:69
translate spanish hwb_s04_f4f3554d:

    # "I bet somewhere all the big shots from that publishing house are gathered up in their corporate tower, laughing at the idiots they’ve ripped off with that book."
    "Apuesto a que en algún lugar todos los peces gordos de esa editorial están reunidos en su torre corporativa, riéndose de los idiotas a los que han estafado con ese libro."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:71
translate spanish hwb_s04_a20cefa7:

    # "..."
    "..."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:73
translate spanish hwb_s04_a176fd1f:

    # "Christ, I’m even starting to sound like him."
    "Dios, hasta estoy empezando a sonar como él."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:79
translate spanish hwb_s04_cb2881a1:

    # "The music turns to static before the cassette is silenced by a loud click."
    "La música se convierte en estática antes de que el casete se silencie con un clic fuerte."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:83
translate spanish hwb_s04_bcaa0561:

    # "I eject it and reach for his old tape again. Marina notices, taking the opportunity to break the long held silence."
    "Lo expulso y alcanzo su casete viejo otra vez. Marina lo nota, aprovechando la oportunidad para romper el largo silencio."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:87
translate spanish hwb_s04_6f272346:

    # Marina "So, do you like music a lot?"
    Marina "Так ты сильно любишь музыку?"

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:91
translate spanish hwb_s04_43ba9a15:

    # Amber "Oh, uh, yeah. I guess."
    Amber "О, да. Думаю, да."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:97
translate spanish hwb_s04_48879b96:

    # Marina "I figured. You’ve been playing those tapes this entire time."
    Marina "Заметно. Ты слушаешь эти кассеты постоянно."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:102
translate spanish hwb_s04_c2abf94c:

    # "She picks up one of the tapes on the center console and inspects it, going as far as to poke her pinky through one of the holes."
    "Toma uno de los casetes de la consola central y lo inspecciona, llegando incluso a meter su meñique por uno de los agujeros."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:106
translate spanish hwb_s04_21dfafba:

    # Marina "Though I’m not sure what you’d call this type of music."
    Marina "Я, правда, не уверена насчет жанра."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:110
translate spanish hwb_s04_b23e3bb9:

    # Amber "Yeah, I’ve just been playing whatever. Mostly jazz fusion and alt country. Threw some new age crap in there for good measure."
    Amber "Да у меня вечно играет все подряд. В основном джаз-фьюжн и альт-кантри. Ну и немного нью-эйджа в довесок, чтобы как-то сгладить разницу."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:114
translate spanish hwb_s04_7ec3f766:

    # Amber "Heh. Most of these are mixtapes I made when I was little."
    Amber "Хех. Большинство этих кассет я записала в детстве."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:120
translate spanish hwb_s04_7453e7a7:

    # Marina "Cool! Any names I’d recognize?"
    Marina "Круто! А я знаю каких-нибудь исполнителей из тех, кого ты слушаешь?"

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:122
translate spanish hwb_s04_715c6d3e:

    # "She peeks at me through the holes of the cassette, wearing a wide, genuine smile."
    "Me mira a través de los agujeros del casete, con una sonrisa amplia y genuina."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:126
translate spanish hwb_s04_e4accaca:

    # Amber "Probably not."
    Amber "Скорее всего, нет."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:128
translate spanish hwb_s04_48045a05:

    # Marina "Aww, Come on, try me!"
    Marina "Оуууу. Ну давай, испытай меня."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:132
translate spanish hwb_s04_3ef958a5:

    # "Eh, why not? Maybe I’m not giving her enough credit."
    "Eh, ¿por qué no? Quizás no le estoy dando suficiente crédito."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:134
translate spanish hwb_s04_1d7b5ea1:

    # Amber "You know, Gabriel, Gurtu, Weather Report, Donovan, Metheny…"
    Amber "Итак, знаешь ли ты Питера Гэбриэла, Трилока Гурту, «Weather Report», Донована Филипса, Патрика Мэтини..."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:138
translate spanish hwb_s04_ad8eb67b:

    # "Marina gives sage-like nods and grunts of understanding as I list off the names."
    "Marina asiente con sabiduría y gruñe en señal de comprensión mientras enumero los nombres."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:142
translate spanish hwb_s04_60b91b04:

    # Amber "You have no idea who any of them are, do you?"
    Amber "Ты ведь понятия не имеешь кто это, да?"

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:144
translate spanish hwb_s04_9faf0663:

    # Marina "Not a clue."
    Marina "Ни капли."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:146
translate spanish hwb_s04_fb29e6f5:

    # Amber "That’s what I thought."
    Amber "Об этом я и говорила.."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:150
translate spanish hwb_s04_3bff2708:

    # Marina "Sorry… I usually listen to whatever is on the radio."
    Marina "Прости... Обычно я просто слушаю что-нибудь по радио."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:154
translate spanish hwb_s04_ccf5840e:

    # "I crack a slight smile."
    "Esbozo una leve sonrisa."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:158
translate spanish hwb_s04_5dbe5450:

    # Amber "It’s alright. I could see how it might be hard to get into."
    Amber "Все в порядке. Я знала, что будет трудно угадать."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:162
translate spanish hwb_s04_b55674e9:

    # Amber "My Gramps used to call it ‘road trip music.’"
    Amber "Мой дедушка называл это “музыкой для путешествий”."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:166
translate spanish hwb_s04_aa70bd0f:

    # Marina "I still think it’s nice, though. It’s making you really happy!"
    Marina "Я думаю, что это замечательно, ведь она делает тебя по-настоящему счастливой!"

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:170
translate spanish hwb_s04_7ffb624e:

    # Amber "You think so?"
    Amber "Ты правда так считаешь?"

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:174
translate spanish hwb_s04_a3d4b4d0:

    # "She taps her finger gently against my cheek. I pull away a little, but let her do it anyway."
    "Ella toca suavemente mi mejilla con un dedo. Me aparto un poco, pero la dejo hacerlo de todas formas."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:178
translate spanish hwb_s04_2bbfcb73:

    # Marina "Yeah! Why else would you be smiling?"
    Marina "Даа! Иначе почему ты улыбаешься?"

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:182
translate spanish hwb_s04_bc09a3bc:

    # "I’ve never really thought of whether it made me happy before, but I do know it made him happy, so that’s good enough for me."
    "Nunca me había preguntado si me hacía feliz, pero sé que a él lo hacía feliz, así que eso es suficiente para mí."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:186
translate spanish hwb_s04_c6e86ac4:

    # Amber "That's actually why I'm going to California. You know, for a music festival."
    Amber "На самом деле, из-за этого я еду в Калифорнию. Ну, знаешь, там музыкальный фестиваль."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:190
translate spanish hwb_s04_be97d881:

    # Marina "For real? Where?"
    Marina "Правда? Где?"

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:194
translate spanish hwb_s04_765af23c:

    # Amber "Not far from Palm Springs."
    Amber "Не далеко от Палм Спрингс."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:196
translate spanish hwb_s04_bc44ca5e:

    # Marina "Palm Springs? Like, the actual Palm Springs?"
    Marina "Палм Спринс? Тот самый Палм Спрингс?"

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:199
translate spanish hwb_s04_d34d4345:

    # Amber "Of course. Isn't that where all the lesbian couples go?"
    Amber "Именно. Разве не туда едут все влюбленные лесбиянки?"

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:201
translate spanish hwb_s04_eda790e8:

    # Marina "Too early in the story for that."
    Marina "Мне кажется, нам пока что рано об этом говорить."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:203
translate spanish hwb_s04_f11d52dc:

    # Amber "Right."
    Amber "Верно."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:206
translate spanish hwb_s04_5861f9a1:

    # Amber "Don’t know if there are any other Palm Springs in California, but yeah. They do it every year for a few weekends."
    Amber "Не знаю, есть ли другие Палм Спрингс в Калифорнии, но да. Они туда каждый год приезжают на несколько выходных."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:208
translate spanish hwb_s04_90dcc250:

    # Marina "I went to my first concert a little ago before I graduated."
    Marina "Я однажды была на концерте, незадолго до того как закончила школу."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:212
translate spanish hwb_s04_18db4f36:

    # "She rests her head against the window and stares at the road ahead, her smile fading but still there."
    "Apoya la cabeza contra la ventanilla y mira fijamente el camino frente a nosotras, su sonrisa se desvanece pero aún permanece."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:214
translate spanish hwb_s04_8792fd21:

    # Marina "It was so much fun…"
    Marina "Было так весело…"

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:216
translate spanish hwb_s04_8706d8ea:

    # Marina "An entire weekend of that sounds super awesome."
    Marina "Все выходные. Это звучит круто!"

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:218
translate spanish hwb_s04_20fbcec9:

    # Amber "Nah, it ain’t that cool."
    Amber "Меех. Не так уж круто."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:222
translate spanish hwb_s04_df8ddd2c:

    # "Marina flings her head away from the window and turns to me."
    "Marina aparta la cabeza de la ventanilla de golpe y se vuelve hacia mí."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:224
translate spanish hwb_s04_33ff2d7a:

    # "Now she’s staring at {i}me{/i} like I’m crazy."
    "Ahora me mira a {i}mí{/i} como si estuviera loca."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:226
translate spanish hwb_s04_a0d6d443:

    # Marina "How could you even say that? It’s the coolest thing ever! I wouldn’t even be able to wait. I’d want to see all the bands!"
    Marina "Как ты могла такое сказать? Это же ведь лучшее, что может быть на свете! Я бы так хотела увидеть все эти группы!"

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:232
translate spanish hwb_s04_e5f7cfae:

    # Amber "Sheesh, relax. It’s not like I’m taking it for granted. It’s just that there’s only one group I know I wanna see so far."
    Amber "Боже мой, не заводись ты так. Просто там есть одна группа, которую я очень хочу увидеть."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:236
translate spanish hwb_s04_0fb76f65:

    # "That’s right. His favorite group."
    "Así es. Su grupo favorito."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:240
translate spanish hwb_s04_648a616b:

    # Marina "Just one?"
    Marina "Всего одна?"

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:242
translate spanish hwb_s04_695df566:

    # "He was so excited when he got the tickets."
    "Estaba tan emocionado cuando consiguió los boletos."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:244
translate spanish hwb_s04_314ba755:

    # Amber "Just one that I'm excited for. I'll watch a bunch though."
    Amber "Только одна, которой я буду рада. Хотя и остальных я послушаю."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:248
translate spanish hwb_s04_abbebb14:

    # "Releasing a long sigh, Marina eases back into her seat."
    "Soltando un largo suspiro, Marina se recuesta en su asiento."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:250
translate spanish hwb_s04_7bf66b80:

    # Marina "Oh good. I was afraid you were going to head on home after you saw your group."
    Marina "Ну и славно. А я уже испугалась, что ты сразу поедешь домой, как только увидишь свою любимую группу."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:254
translate spanish hwb_s04_a9d005f9:

    # Amber "You crazy? I’d like to at least have a little fun before worrying about all the expenses I gotta deal with."
    Amber "Ты с ума сошла? Я же должна буду хоть немного расслабиться перед тем как начать разбираться со своими долгами..."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:258
translate spanish hwb_s04_28d2e6ad:

    # Marina "Expenses?"
    Marina "Долгами?"

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:262
translate spanish hwb_s04_758a8556:

    # "Dammit."
    "Maldición."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:264
translate spanish hwb_s04_6d3e80e4:

    # Amber "Ah, it’s nothing."
    Amber "Оу, ничего, забудь."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:268
translate spanish hwb_s04_8261f6d4:

    # "She gasps."
    "Ella jadea."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:272
translate spanish hwb_s04_0f76c9b1:

    # Marina "Are you in debt? Is it college loans? My brother said those aren’t fun to deal with at all."
    Marina "Ты в долгах?  За колледж? Мой брат говорил, что с этим лучше не сталкиваться."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:274
translate spanish hwb_s04_e55e020a:

    # "Got too comfortable. Should have just kept my trap shut."
    "Me confié demasiado. Debí haberme callado la boca."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:276
translate spanish hwb_s04_17c356b5:

    # Marina "Or… did you just spend too much on your ticke—"
    Marina "Или… ты потратила слишком много на биле—"

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:281
translate spanish hwb_s04_ea6af1f8:

    # "Without warning, I swerve off to the side of the road and on to the rocky sand, cutting Marina off and nearly giving her a heart attack." with vpunch
    "Без всякого предупреждения, я резко сворачиваю с дороги на песок и камни, прерывая тем самым Маринин вопрос и чуть не заставляя ее сердце остановиться." with vpunch

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:285
translate spanish hwb_s04_fd0efd4a:

    # "Marina shoots me a worried glance, her face still pale."
    "Marina me lanza una mirada preocupada, aún pálida."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:287
translate spanish hwb_s04_e11750ba:

    # Marina "Oh my god! What was that, are you okay?"
    Marina "О боже мой! Что с тобой, ты в порядке?"

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:291
translate spanish hwb_s04_4c245843:

    # "I pinch the bridge of my nose and my elbows on the wheel."
    "Me pellizco el puente de la nariz y apoyo los codos en el volante."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:293
translate spanish hwb_s04_252ed066:

    # Marina "Amber?"
    Marina "Эмбер?"

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:295
translate spanish hwb_s04_639dd99d:

    # Amber "I’ve been driving all day. I’m a little tired."
    Amber "Я весь день за рулем. Немного устала."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:297
translate spanish hwb_s04_06568959:

    # Marina "Where are we?"
    Marina "Где мы сейчас?"

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:299
translate spanish hwb_s04_b5293baf:

    # Amber "A little outside Albuquerque, so we aren’t too far now."
    Amber "Мы совсем рядом с Альбукерке, так что осталось немного."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:301
translate spanish hwb_s04_a98aa305:

    # Amber "We’ll sleep here tonight and drive to Shiprock first thing in the morning."
    Amber "Заночуем здесь, а утром сразу же отправимся в Шипрок."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:343
translate spanish hwb_s04_b54f1ea9:

    # "Killing the ignition, I climb out of my seat and into the living quarters. Marina trails behind me."
    "Apago el motor, salgo de mi asiento y paso a la sala de estar. Marina me sigue detrás."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:345
translate spanish hwb_s04_ae5a5fe7:

    # "I yank open the bathroom's velcro latched cupboards."
    "Abro de golpe los armarios de velcro del baño."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:347
translate spanish hwb_s04_437e132b:

    # "Inside is a folded stack with a blanket, sheet, pillow, and my old gym clothes from school. I scoop them up and toss them to Marina. She scrambles to catch it, desperately balancing them as they lean out of her arms."
    "Dentro hay una pila doblada con una manta, una sábana, una almohada y mi ropa vieja de gimnasia del colegio. Las recojo y se las lanzo a Marina. Ella forcejea para atraparlas, equilibrando desesperadamente el montón que se le escapa de los brazos."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:349
translate spanish hwb_s04_1b897584:

    # Amber "Sorry about the clothes. I don’t have any actual pajamas."
    Amber "Прости за такую одежду. У меня просто нет пижамы."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:353
translate spanish hwb_s04_38276b7f:

    # Amber "You can sleep on the couch. It folds out into a bed."
    Amber "Ты можешь спать на кушетке, ее можно разложить в кровать."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:357
translate spanish hwb_s04_6c62f45e:

    # Marina "Oh… Okay."
    Marina "Оу... Хорошо."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:359
translate spanish hwb_s04_9f49e4d7:

    # Amber "Alright then, see you in the morning."
    Amber "Ну вот и все, до утра."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:367
translate spanish hwb_s04_a08dda4f:

    # "With that, I step into the back room and slam the sliding door, before collapsing onto the oversized bed."
    "Dicho esto, entro al cuarto trasero y cierro de golpe la puerta corrediza, antes de desplomarme en la cama enorme."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:369
translate spanish hwb_s04_b5bfc241:

    # "Even in the darkness I can make out the pictures hanging on the wall. Once upon a time, they were generic scenic pieces. Now they’re photos. Photos of me and Gramps."
    "Incluso en la oscuridad puedo distinguir los cuadros colgados en la pared. Érase una vez, eran piezas escénicas genéricas. Ahora son fotos. Fotos mías y del Abuelo."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:393
translate spanish hwb_s04_2ac86051:

    # "My favorite is the one of us in front of a museum for music. Rock and roll, to be specific."
    "Mi favorita es la de nosotros frente a un museo de música. De rock and roll, para ser exactos."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:404
translate spanish hwb_s04_87ab21e0:

    # "I was just a little pipsqueak back then, holding up an autographed vinyl sleeve that was about the size of my head."
    "Yo era solo una pequeña renacuaja en ese entonces, sosteniendo una funda de vinilo autografiada que era casi del tamaño de mi cabeza."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:406
translate spanish hwb_s04_ef05b6d8:

    # "He was by my side, squatting down and ruffling my hair as I gave the biggest smile I could—even with my missing teeth."
    "Él estaba a mi lado, agachándose y revolviéndome el pelo mientras yo sonreía lo más grande que podía, incluso con los dientes faltantes."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:408
translate spanish hwb_s04_be7a83e9:

    # "I let out a sigh and fixate on the ceilings skylight, a small sliver of the moonlight shining through."
    "Suelto un suspiro y me fijo en el tragaluz del techo, un pequeño destello de luz de luna brillando a través."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:410
translate spanish hwb_s04_b7ecadf5:

    # "It feels like an eternity since I’ve last laid down in this bed. I remember it felt like being hugged by a cloud. Now it feels like concrete."
    "Siento que ha pasado una eternidad desde la última vez que me acosté en esta cama. Recuerdo que se sentía como un abrazo de una nube. Ahora se siente como concreto."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:416
translate spanish hwb_s04_4df1ee48:

    # "Tiny creaks sound from the room next door, accompanied by Marina's little squeaks of determination as she struggles with the foldout bed. Until finally, I hear a loud thud."
    "Pequeños crujidos suenan desde la habitación de al lado, acompañados de los diminutos gruñidos de determinación de Marina mientras forcejea con la cama plegable. Hasta que, finalmente, escucho un fuerte golpe."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:424
translate spanish hwb_s04_09c534e0:

    # Marina "Agh!"
    Marina "Аргхх!"

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:426
translate spanish hwb_s04_b32c09dd:

    # "I can’t help but smirk a little."
    "No puedo evitar esbozar una sonrisita."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:428
translate spanish hwb_s04_6195c84d:

    # "I should’ve warned her that it was heavy."
    "Debí haberle advertido que era pesada."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:430
translate spanish hwb_s04_001ce877:

    # "The room over goes silent."
    "La habitación de al lado se queda en silencio."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:432
translate spanish hwb_s04_2e9d16f1:

    # "I hope it didn’t crush her."
    "Espero que no la haya aplastado."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:434
translate spanish hwb_s04_22bb5efc:

    # "Luckily, I soon hear footsteps tiptoeing across the carpet, then on the bathroom tile. They stop outside my door."
    "Por suerte, pronto escucho pasos de puntillas sobre la alfombra, luego sobre el azulejo del baño. Se detienen frente a mi puerta."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:436
translate spanish hwb_s04_6af6be55:

    # Marina "Hey, are you awake?"
    Marina "Эй, ты спишь?"

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:438
translate spanish hwb_s04_368864c5:

    # "Her voice is weak, barely above a whisper. It’s almost impossible to hear as it’s muffled through the door."
    "Su voz es débil, apenas un susurro. Es casi imposible de oír por lo amortiguada que está a través de la puerta."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:440
translate spanish hwb_s04_58a661e5:

    # Marina "I know I’ve said it a lot already, but I really mean it. Thanks, Amber."
    Marina "Я знаю, что так много раз говорила это за день, но я и правда тебе благодарна. Спасибо, Эмбер."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:442
translate spanish hwb_s04_19f81664:

    # Marina "Goodnight."
    Marina "Доброй ночи."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:444
translate spanish hwb_s04_1037bf9a:

    # "I continue to stay silent. In the dark, the ceiling looks like it’s constantly changing in size and dimension, sometimes getting bigger and further away, other times getting closer and smaller."
    "Sigo en silencio. En la oscuridad, el techo parece cambiar constantemente de tamaño y dimensión, a veces haciéndose más grande y lejano, otras veces más cercano y pequeño."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:446
translate spanish hwb_s04_71172d27:

    # "I look down. Through the crack under the door I can see her shadow turning around to leave."
    "Miro hacia abajo. Por la rendija debajo de la puerta, veo su sombra dándose la vuelta para irse."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:448
translate spanish hwb_s04_40ac41e3:

    # "The words slip out of my mouth before she can even take her first step."
    "Las palabras se escapan de mi boca antes de que ella pueda dar su primer paso."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:450
translate spanish hwb_s04_596d4ca0:

    # Amber "‘Night, kiddo."
    Amber "Доброй, малышка."

# game/script/hwb_s04.rpy:408
translate spanish hwb_s04_7599c3a6:

    # "I let out a sigh and fixate on the ceiling's skylight, a small sliver of the moonlight shining through."
    "Suelto un suspiro y me fijo en la claraboya del techo, un pequeño destello de luz lunar brillando a través de ella."

